msgid ""
"You gain a +1 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this magic "
"weapon. The bonus increases to +3 when you use the mace to attack a "
"construct.    \n"
"When you roll a 20 on an attack roll made with this weapon, the target takes "
"an extra 2d6 bludgeoning damage, or 4d6 bludgeoning damage if it's a "
"construct. If a construct has 25 hit points or fewer after taking this "
"damage, it is destroyed. \n"
